          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（诸葛亮上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忠心扶汉王，南阳美丈夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣，诸葛亮见驾，愿吾皇万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐座。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座。宣山人上殿，有何国事议论？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人夜得一梦，请先生上殿详解。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公得何梦兆，待臣详解。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "寡人梦见二弟浑身是血，不知主何吉凶？"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣告便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀且住，山人昨夜仰观天象，见一斗大红星坠落西北，主公又得此梦，应在"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二千岁归天。待我朦胧启奏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启主公：日有所思，夜有所梦。想是主公思念二千岁心胜矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生，二弟若有差迟，吾命休矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启主公：廖化披头散发，午门候旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣他上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣廖化上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廖化上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "山崩地裂事，报与主公知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀万岁爷吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "廖化为何披头散发，这等光景？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二千岁命丧玉泉山！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二千岁命丧玉泉山！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听说二弟丧玉泉，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "魂飞天涯不拢边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心中犹如乱箭攒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "廖化，二千岁因何归天？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "雨打梨花分落瓣"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "东吴人马白衣渡江，二千岁命丧玉泉山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就该到上鄘搬兵求救。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣已曾到上鄘搬兵，怎奈刘封、孟达按兵不动。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快到阆中报与三千岁知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "廖化",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（廖化下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生，刘封、孟达按兵不出，理应将他二人治罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "事急有变，且缓图之。还要加升他二人官职才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此传孤旨意：加升刘封为绵竹郡主，即日来京，共议报仇之策。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公明见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生，还要发兵与孤二弟报仇才是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "诸葛亮",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今冬发兵，不利我国。等待明春发兵，必要大获全胜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若待明春报仇，寡人心中难消恶气。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泪汪汪吩咐且退班，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咬牙切齿骂孙权。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘备",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼睁睁一旦失桃园。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘备、诸葛亮同下。）"
        }
      ],
