        "旗牌"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四文堂引刘封同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "镇守引胜关，儿郎心胆寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣旨下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启千岁：圣旨下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看香案伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（旗牌上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣旨下，跪听宣读。诏曰：“刘封镇守边关，受尽风霜。圣上见喜，封为绵竹"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "郡主。命尔带领人马，擒拿孟达，候有功再赏。即日回京，共议报仇之策。”"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "圣旨读罢，望诏谢恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万万岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请过圣旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "香案供奉。不知大人驾到，未曾远迎，多多有罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吩咐后堂摆宴。"
        },
        {
          "character": "旗牌",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君命在身，不敢久停。就此回朝复命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此送过大人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。旗牌下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马班师回朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
