    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘封",
        "四文堂",
        "四札头",
        "孟达"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四札头引孟达同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟达",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当初一时错，如今后悔迟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，孟达。只因二千岁命丧玉泉山，廖化前来搬兵。是我按兵不出，因此弃蜀"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "归魏。今有刘封提兵到此，不免说他降魏便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四札头",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起兵前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四札头",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四文堂引刘封同上，会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！胆大孟达，前番失我叔父之义，今日又来则甚！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，小千岁请息怒，末将有言告禀：想主公立了阿斗守阙东宫，小千岁作了分"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟达",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外之人。依末将相劝，弃蜀归魏，不失封侯之位。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一派胡言，放马过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘封、孟达同开打，刘封败下，孟达追下。四札头同下。刘封上，四文堂同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀败了，杀败了！你看孟达甚是骁勇，这便如何是好？也罢，不免回朝搬兵报"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仇便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘封",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马班师回朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四文堂",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
